%N A183648 Number of (n+1) X 6 0..4 arrays with every 2 X 2 subblock summing to 8.
%H A183648 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A183648/b183648.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000</a> (terms 1..84 from R. H. Hardin).
