%H A183648 <a href="/index/Rec#order_05">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (15,-85,225,-274,120).
%F A183648 a(n) = 15*a(n-1) - 85*a(n-2) + 225*a(n-3) - 274*a(n-4) + 120*a(n-5).
%F A183648 G.f.: x*(25405 - 330950*x + 1524203*x^2 - 2897770*x^3 + 1875000*x^4) / ((1 - x)*(1 - 2*x)*(1 - 3*x)*(1 - 4*x)*(1 - 5*x)). - _Colin Barker_, Apr 01 2018
%F A183648 a(n) = 5*5^n + 248*4^n + 1806*3^n + 5404*2^n + 8162. - _Christian Krause_, Jun 12 2026
%e A183648 Some solutions for 3 X 6:
%e A183648   4 4 1 1 1 1    2 0 0 2 2 3    4 4 2 1 0 1    2 3 0 2 1 1
%e A183648   0 0 3 3 3 3    2 4 4 2 2 1    0 0 2 3 4 3    1 2 3 3 2 4
%e A183648   4 4 1 1 1 1    2 0 0 2 2 3    4 4 2 1 0 1    2 3 0 2 1 1
%t A183648 A183648[n_] := 5*5^n + 248*4^n + 1806*3^n + 5404*2^n + 8162;
